pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `activetrips` ( `username` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `location` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `startdate` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `enddate` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `tourguide` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `tripid` varchar(15) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`tripid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `admin` ( `username` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `location` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `gender` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL, `facebook` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `github` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `linkedin` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`username`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `booking` ( `packageid` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `packagename` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `location` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `price` int(20) NOT NULL, `username` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `name` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `tourguideid` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`packageid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `discounts` ( `id` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `specialDiscount` int(25) DEFAULT 0, `fixedCard` int(25) DEFAULT 0, `fixedCoupon` int(25) DEFAULT 0, `date` varchar(25) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=18 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `earnings` ( `travelers` int(255) NOT NULL, `hotels` int(255) NOT NULL, `advertisement` int(255) NOT NULL, `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `expenses` ( `tourguides` int(255) NOT NULL, `officestuff` int(255) NOT NULL, `others` int(255) NOT NULL, `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `notification` ( `name` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `transaction` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `amount` varchar(10) NOT NULL, `network` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `orderid` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `date` varchar(25) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`orderid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `ratings` ( `username` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `time` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `comment` text NOT NULL, `rating` varchar(6) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT './UserImage/travelers.png', `email` varchar(30) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`username`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `revenuetable` ( `country` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `users` int(255) NOT NULL, `transactions` int(255) NOT NULL, `revenue` int(255) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`country`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `service` ( `name` varchar(500) NOT NULL, `catagory` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL, `destination` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL, `deprature` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `details` varchar(10000) DEFAULT NULL, `price` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL, `stock` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL, `rating` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL, `imgsource` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`name`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `totalplans` ( `id` int(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `price` int(255) NOT NULL, `quantity` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tourguide` ( `username` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `location` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `joiningdate` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `phone` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL, `salary` varchar(15) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`username`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `travelers` ( `username` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `location` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `joiningdate` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `phone` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`username`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

table.column: Cox's Bazar Tour Package: Package Name: Beach Bliss Duration: 3 Days / 2 Nights Price: $300 per person Highlights: Accommodation in a beachfront resort Guided tours to Cox's Bazar beach, Inani Beach, and Himchari National Park Sunset watching at Cox's Bazar beach Traditional seafood dinner Bonfire night with cultural performances Complimentary breakfast and lunch included Package Name: Adventure Escape Duration: 4 Days / 3 Nights Price: $450 per person Highlights: Exciting water sports activities including surfing, jet skiing, and banana boat ride Trekking to Himchari National Park Beach camping experience under the stars Snorkeling at St. Martin's Island Island hopping tour to nearby islands Authentic seafood barbecue dinner Comfortable accommodation in beach cottages
